<item>
            <title>[HBASE-15995] Separate replication WAL reading from shipping</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-15995</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently ReplicationSource reads edits from the WAL and ships them in the same thread.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;By breaking out the reading from the shipping, we can introduce greater parallelism and lay the foundation for further refactoring to a pipelined, streaming model.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
